<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Students Support Environment at Focus the Nation Event</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Courtney Gilmartin
		
		<span class="date">Jan. 31, 2008</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 0px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1311/en_US/crottycrop.jpg" height="0" width="0"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>Orange County Mayor Rich Crotty toured the green roof on the UCF Student Union on Thursday during his visit to UCF. Crotty spoke with Marty Wanielista, right, director of the UCF Stormwater Management Academy.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=0024004144fcb4b10117ade51f2a0078b7">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
